data.description: Great location for this 1.1 Acres potential commercial corner lot.   Bring your contractor or builder to make this a residential home or great commercial opportunity.  Formerly a personal care home, but can be a great daycare, office suites, new construction townhouses, endless opportunities. This lot has two entrances from Blair Bridge & Oak Ridge Rds. Easy access to I-20 & the Airport via Thornton Rd. Come see this 3+ br/3 full ba property. A rare find with a full finished basement w/2 rooms, full bath(needs work), storage rm, full kitchen & separate interior & exterior entrances. This makes for an amazing AirBNB or Home Healthcare Facility, etc. Property is being sold as-is. Don't miss out on this much land space in the city, where you can potentially have a live and work opportunity.
